title: Timothy Abramov
text: Hi, I’m Tim, nice to meet you! Currently I am studying Data Science at New College of Florida. I use R and Python for my data-driven endeavors, and particularly enjoy data visualization and munging. In my leisure time I sing in a church choir, go for hikes, and dabble in leather craft.

title: Hi and welcome!
text:
Hi and welcome, I’m Tim, nice to meet you!





Long story short, here is a plan of mine in a nutshell:









With this blog I hope to improve my abilities in:

writing (travel/story blogs, tutorials, coding adventures)
coding prowess (R, Python)
marketing abilities

I’ve got a long journey ahead of me, hope to see you in the next one!
Tim
